article_title: Bristol Palin and Dakota Meyer Call Off Wedding
article_text:
BY:



Bristol Palin and Dakota Meyer have called off their wedding, according to a Facebook post by Sarah Palin.

The two were set to marry May 23, but the wedding will no longer take place. The two announced their engagement in March.

Meyer is a U.S. Marine veteran who was awarded a Medal of Honor for his actions in Afghanistan. Bristol Palin is the daughter of vice presidential candidate Sarah Palin.

According to Sarah Palin’s Facebook post:
